Toyako.title: Toyako
Toyako.byline: Toyako (洞爺湖町) is a city in Hokkaido's Shikotsu-Toya National Park.

Toyama.title: Toyama
Toyama.byline: Toyama (富山) is the capital of Toyama prefecture, Japan.

Toyama (prefecture).title: Toyama (prefecture)
Toyama (prefecture).byline: Toyama Prefecture (富山県 Toyama-ken) is in the central Chubu region of the main Japanese island Honshu.

Toyohashi.title: Toyohashi
Toyohashi.byline: Toyohashi (豊橋) is a city in Aichi prefecture in Honshu, Japan.

Toyooka.title: Toyooka
Toyooka.byline: Toyooka is a city in Hyogo.

Toyota.title: Toyota
Toyota.byline: Toyota (豊田) is the largest city in Aichi Prefecture by area, and the sixth largest city in the entire Chūbu region by population.
